title: DAO #12 - DAO Fund distribution
body:
At the moment, the DAO fund has accumulated from 9 auctions on NFTL.art

62323 NFTL

We also plan to hold 10 auctions, where the NFT buyer will get a unique opportunity

Receive% from every SAVENFT transaction for a whole year!

We will redeem NFTL & CTF and send part of these tokens to the NFT holders.

Which% receive NFT holder?
Genesis - 5%
Legendary - 1%
Epic - 0.1%
Rare - 0.01%

The set of the collection remains the same, but price changes:

- Genesis - 1M NFTL
- Legendary - 300k NFTL
- Epic - 50k NFTL 
- Rare - 7.5k NFTL

How do we distribute tokens in the DAO Fund?
